data.title: Sis Yem Hayvancilik Nakliye Tarim Urunleri Hububat Gubre Ith Company Profile - Turkiye
data.text: Sis Yem Hayvancilik Nakliye Tarim Urunleri Hububat Gubre Ith Ihr San Tic Ltd Sti is based in Turkiye. The head office is in Adana. The enterprise operates in the Other Animal Food Manufacturing industry. Sis Yem Hayvancilik Nakliye Tarim Urunleri Hububat Gubre Ith Ihr San Tic Ltd Sti was incorporated on July 22, 2008. 14 (2020) employees currently work for Sis Yem Hayvancilik Nakliye Tarim Urunleri Hububat Gubre Ith Ihr San Tic Ltd Sti.
